    "A formalist, his methodology employed a \"cyclical development of forms\" theory in the manner of <a href=\"/wolfflinh\">Heinrich W\u00f6lfflin</a> (Bazin) and Adolf von Hildebrand, an approach that has not, as a rule, stood the test of time.": [],
